headline: Online scam uses fake ICE raids at Target and Walmart to steal personal data
summary: Viral TikTok videos claiming retail workers were deported or fired by ICE are part of a phishing scam designed to collect email addresses, phone numbers, and payment information.

headline: 3 Big Reasons to Love Lululemon (LULU)
summary: What a brutal six months it’s been for Lululemon. The stock has dropped 52.3% and now trades at $196.75, rattling many shareholders. This was partly driven by its softer quarterly results and might have investors contemplating their next move.
